{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162857, "create_time": 1653762855, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我不知道啊，可能是我太寂寞了", "timestamp": 1653762855}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162883, "create_time": 1653763091, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 人类被期望忍受寂寞。寻求外界来填充自己是危险的做法。", "timestamp": 1653763091}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162886, "create_time": 1653763131, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 那怎么办呢", "timestamp": 1653763131}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162924, "create_time": 1653763488, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 忍受，到习惯。以及权衡风险与收益，将自己抽离在外理性地考虑满足自己寂寞的得与失，或许会更容易习惯。至少我现在是这样。当然或许还有一些平日里的思考以及娱乐作为帮助。", "timestamp": 1653763488}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162934, "create_time": 1653763577, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 做不到，好难，哭", "timestamp": 1653763577}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162940, "create_time": 1653763642, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 当然，或许也有那种，内心永远坚强，灿烂，像太阳一样的人。或者所谓认识到世界黑暗却依然热爱生活的勇者。可惜我并不算，也不知道如何成为那种人。", "timestamp": 1653763642}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162945, "create_time": 1653763738, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 你也可以只是期望自己的运气够好，一下子就可以找到理解自己的人。或者至少抱有这样的希望。有希望的人生总是有盼头的", "timestamp": 1653763738}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162968, "create_time": 1653763909, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 也不一定非要理解自己，像洞主这种开导式也很好。就是会很需要和别人聊天，从而疏散自己的emo。（不是说给人倾倒负面情绪，就是听听别人的日常生活就很好）", "timestamp": 1653763909}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162970, "create_time": 1653763913, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "所以很明显，我只是藉此随便说些关于自己的有的没的话，收获什么样的回答我都不惊讶。", "timestamp": 1653763913}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162986, "create_time": 1653764030, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 前后有什么联系吗", "timestamp": 1653764030}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 162991, "create_time": 1653764059, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 其实平日里我倒是不怎么聊天的。如果能对你有帮助那我很荣幸，毕竟不过是些胡言乱语罢了。", "timestamp": 1653764059}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 163002, "create_time": 1653764126, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 感觉你的逻辑很自恰，而我的痛苦根源大概来自于我的行为不能符合我的逻辑，我的能力不能达到我的期望。", "timestamp": 1653764126}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 163006, "create_time": 1653764170, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 我在写回答时并不会实时刷新，所以你看到的许多可能是我对你上一句话的回应。我并不是很理解你所指的“前后”是什么，但一般是有联系的。", "timestamp": 1653764170}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 163017, "create_time": 1653764272, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 这样。但我会很佩服你的做法，习惯寂寞，并且战胜内心的渴求", "timestamp": 1653764272}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 163077, "create_time": 1653764714, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 自洽的原因是由于我的回答大部分都是我曾经考虑过的问题，我会期望我对世界的理解以及价值判断做到统一，最后达到知行合一（没错，其实我是奔着肉身成圣去的）。但当然，作为人类的我依然受限于许多问题，我时常会考虑，但不总是有结果。有时，我也会羡慕那些不怎么考虑这些问题的人。当然，或许我现在的问题在于想得多而看得少、做得少，按知乎的说法，这人就该去读读毛选就好了。至于你的痛苦，想解决无法是骗（让自己认为自己的行为符合逻辑）或者改（改逻辑或改行为）。当然，值得指出的是，骗未必是个坏方法。", "timestamp": 1653764714}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 163080, "create_time": 1653764741, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 最后，我该写作业去了，有缘再会", "timestamp": 1653764741}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 163111, "create_time": 1653764963, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 不错，引起了我的思考！有缘再会！不过这么晚了真的不睡觉吗", "timestamp": 1653764963}], "create_time": 1653762629, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653764963, "likenum": 3, "n_attentions": 3, "n_comments": 17, "pid": 53351, "poll": null, "reply": 17, "text": "在这种地方交友的人类，是寻求理解，还是寻求不理解呢？或者大家还是喜欢兼而有之中庸的调子", "timestamp": 1653762629}}